title: Tattoo Fixers S01E08 720p HDTV.mp4
description:
Tattoo Fixers S01E08 720p HDTV

Three of the nation's most exciting tattoo artists join forces to fix the UK's shocking and shameful tattoo catastrophes. Superstar inkers Sketch, Lou and Jay, along with receptionist Paisley, have the tricky task of fixing and transforming the most extreme, ridiculous and downright hilarious tattoos that arrive at their studio. This week the Tattoo Fixers come to the aid of Victoria, who is in desperate need of a cover-up before she can return to college and train as a teacher. Pensioner Abigail's bucket list puts her in the hands of Sketch, who'll be taking her tattoo virginity at the age of 75. The parlour also gets a visit from Alice who, after being forced to conform in order to get a job, is now desperate to breathe new life back into the tattoos she tried to banish. Lou rids Hollie of her cheeky chicken ink, Sketch helps Lisa divorce a big tattoo mistake, and Jay finally gets to ink Paisley
